    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>General term for a person, group of people, places, things, or concepts that are invented for a particular reason, but not identified or accepted in reality. In the context of art, an "invented entity" could refer to multiple creators that are known by a single pseudonym for a collective project or work.</Note_Text>
